name: No. 8 Breathe Essential Oil
description:
No. 8 Repel Essential Oil, 10 ml

Ingredients: Essential Oils of Sage, Hyssop, Eucalyptus, Spruce, Thyme and Myrtle.

How to Use:great for diffusers and chest congestion. Can also be used in a bath, just pour one cup of coconut milk (or buttermilk if you prefer) into a warm bath, then add 20 drops of your essential Oil (so that the oil does not float to the surface) and enjoy the experience.
